<h1 style="text-align: center; color: #D63384;">QutyClora</h1>

<h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>

<p>We wanted to inform you that the status of your order <strong>{{orderId}}</strong> has been updated to:</p>
<h3 style="color: #007BFF;">{{status}}</h3>

<p>Here’s a summary of your order:</p>

<table border="1" cellpadding="8" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;">
  <thead>
    <tr style="background-color: #f2f2f2;">
      <th>Product</th>
      <th>Qty</th>
      <th>Rate</th>
      <th>Total</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    {{#each items}}
    <tr>
      <td>{{name}}</td>
      <td>{{quantity}}</td>
      <td>₹{{price}}</td>
      <td>₹{{total}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{/each}}
  </tbody>
</table>

<p>
  <strong>Subtotal:</strong> ₹{{subtotal}}<br />
  {{#if discount_name}}
    <strong>Discount ({{discount_name}}):</strong> -₹{{discount_amount}}<br />
  {{/if}}
  <strong>Final Amount Paid:</strong> ₹{{amount}}
</p>

<p><strong>Shipping Address:</strong><br />
  {{address}}<br />
  <strong>Phone:</strong> {{phoneNo}}</p>

<p><small>Order Date: {{date}}</small></p>

<p>Thank you for shopping with <strong>QutyClora</strong>! We hope to see you again soon.</p>
